{"id":49,"date":"2021-10-07T01:09:38","date_gmt":"2021-10-07T01:09:38","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/cagbcprod.wpengine.com\/?page_id=49"},"modified":"2024-01-24T08:43:22","modified_gmt":"2024-01-24T13:43:22","slug":"zero-carbon-building-standard","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/our-work\/certification\/zero-carbon-building-standard\/","title":{"rendered":"Zero Carbon Building Standards"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:0px\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A made-in-Canada solution<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>CAGBC&#8217;s Zero Carbon Building\u2122 (ZCB) standards are a made-in-Canada framework that makes carbon the new measure of building innovation. Among the world&#8217;s first zero-carbon building standards, they recognize the importance of building emissions in reaching national climate commitments. The ZCB standards are an important tool supporting the green building sector&#8217;s efforts to decarbonize Canada&#8217;s buildings. <\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull\" style=\"min-height:326px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-80 has-background-dim\" style=\"background-color:#1a1a1a\"><\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"852\" height=\"740\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1122\" alt=\"Decorative image\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/wgb_tile_1_852x740.jpg\" style=\"object-position:16% 38%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"16% 38%\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/wgb_tile_1_852x740.jpg 852w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/wgb_tile_1_852x740-300x261.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/wgb_tile_1_852x740-768x667.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 852px) 100vw, 852px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-cloud-white-color has-text-color has-large-font-size\"><strong>What is a zero-carbon building?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-cloud-white-color has-text-color\">A zero-carbon building is highly energy-efficient and minimizes greenhouse gas emissions from building materials and operations. Until all emissions can be eliminated, high-quality carbon offsets can be used as a counterbalance.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p>The ZCB standards define low-carbon design and operational performance for buildings. They offer both rigour and flexibility, opening the door for all buildings to minimize their climate impact. Buildings of all types, from office towers to arenas, warehouses, multi-unit residential buildings, and schools, have been certified under the standards.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-layout-2 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-tree-green-color has-text-color\">Two pathways for buildings<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-columns gb-layout-columns-2 gb-2-col-equal\"><div class=\"gb-layout-column-wrap gb-block-layout-column-gap-2 gb-is-responsive-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-column gb-block-layout-column\"><div class=\"gb-block-layout-column-inner\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"592\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/zcb-perf_twocolumn_1280x740_EN-1024x592.jpg\" alt=\"Cover image of the Zero Carbon Building - Performance Standard\" class=\"wp-image-2015\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/zcb-perf_twocolumn_1280x740_EN-1024x592.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/zcb-perf_twocolumn_1280x740_EN-300x173.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/zcb-perf_twocolumn_1280x740_EN-768x444.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/zcb-perf_twocolumn_1280x740_EN.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-column gb-block-layout-column\"><div class=\"gb-block-layout-column-inner\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"zero-carbon-building-standard-performance\" style=\"font-size:26px\"><strong>Zero Carbon Building <strong>\u2013<\/strong> Performance Standard<\/strong> <\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The ZCB-Performance Standard\u2122 is used to demonstrate that a building has achieved zero-carbon operations. It requires verification annually.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/our-work\/certification\/zero-carbon-building-standard\/zero-carbon-building-standard-performance-resources\/\">Learn more<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-columns gb-layout-columns-2 gb-2-col-equal\"><div class=\"gb-layout-column-wrap gb-block-layout-column-gap-2 gb-is-responsive-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-column gb-block-layout-column\"><div class=\"gb-block-layout-column-inner\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"592\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/zcb-design-v3_twocolumn_1280x740_EN-1024x592.jpg\" alt=\"Zero Carbon Building - Design Standard v3 cover art\" class=\"wp-image-5031\" style=\"width:570px;height:330px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/zcb-design-v3_twocolumn_1280x740_EN-1024x592.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/zcb-design-v3_twocolumn_1280x740_EN-300x173.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/zcb-design-v3_twocolumn_1280x740_EN-768x444.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/zcb-design-v3_twocolumn_1280x740_EN.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-column gb-block-layout-column\"><div class=\"gb-block-layout-column-inner\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"zero-carbon-building-standard-design\" style=\"font-size:26px\"><strong><strong>Zero Carbon Building <strong>\u2013<\/strong> Design Standard<\/strong><\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The ZCB-Design Standard\u2122 guides the design of new buildings or retrofits of existing ones. It offers a pathway to ensure buildings can achieve zero-carbon once in operation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/our-work\/certification\/zero-carbon-building-standard\/zcb-design-resources\/\">Learn More<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull has-parallax is-repeated is-style-banner-ads\" style=\"min-height:280px\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-charcoal-grey-background-color has-background-dim-100 has-background-dim\"><\/span><div role=\"img\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1431 has-parallax is-repeated\" style=\"background-position:50% 50%;background-image:url(https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/arrow-pattern-charcoal-grey-v2.png)\"><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-columns gb-layout-columns-3 gb-3-col-equal\"><div class=\"gb-layout-column-wrap gb-block-layout-column-gap-1 gb-is-responsive-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-column gb-block-layout-column\"><div class=\"gb-block-layout-column-inner\"><div class=\"wp-block-acf-stats-counter wp-block-stat-counter spacing-bottom-1 \"><p class=\"wp-block-stat-counter__value has-text-align-center spacing-top-0\" data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"56\" data-decimal=\"0\" data-animation=\"2.5\">56<\/p><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Current ZCB-Performance certifications <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-column gb-block-layout-column\"><div class=\"gb-block-layout-column-inner\"><div class=\"wp-block-acf-stats-counter wp-block-stat-counter spacing-bottom-1 \"><p class=\"wp-block-stat-counter__value has-text-align-center spacing-top-0\" data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"48\" data-decimal=\"0\" data-animation=\"2.5\">48<\/p><\/div>\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">ZCB-Design certifications<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-column gb-block-layout-column gb-is-vertically-aligned-top\"><div class=\"gb-block-layout-column-inner\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"font-size:88px;line-height:0.9\"><strong>3 in 4<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\" style=\"line-height:1.6\">ZCB-Design certifications are fully electrified<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-tree-green-color has-text-color\">Events and education<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/learn\/attend-an-event\/accelerating-to-zero\/\">Accelerating to Zero<\/a> series of events and education are specific to zero-carbon buildings. As Canada ramps up efforts to reduce carbon, the building sector must have the knowledge and skills necessary to build to zero and to take advantage of the new opportunities afforded by our new, low-carbon economy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-main\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-tree-green-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/learn\/attend-an-event\/accelerating-to-zero\/\">Learn MORE<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover alignfull is-light is-style-banner-ads\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-ocean-blue-background-color has-background-dim-100 has-background-dim\"><\/span><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-607\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/banner-LEED-hours-scaled.webp\" style=\"object-position:90% 69%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"90% 69%\"\/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-cloud-white-color has-text-color has-h-9-font-size\">Looking for Zero Carbon education?  <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-layout-4 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-cloud-white-color has-text-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/www.cagbc.org\/learn\/attend-an-event\/accelerating-to-zero\/\">Learn more<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-tree-green-color has-text-color\"><strong>Need more convincing?<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-te